name: 10 Count Pink Shabby Chic Headband Kit - Baby Shower
description:
Headband kits ship the week prior to the event. 

For a Baby Shower this is a great way for the Mom-To-Be to take home great headbands made with love by all the shower guest. 

Items MAILED to you:
- 10 Elastic (Baby Shower: 0-3, 3-6, 6-9, 9 Months+ )
- 10 Felt Circles 
- 5 Flowers 
- 5 Rosette 
- 5 Little Feathers 

Items EMAILED to you: 
• Photo directions 
• Written directions 
• Items you will need at the baby shower
• 10 Tags with sizes 0-3, 3-6, 6-9, 9+Months and place for guest to sign name 
• Sign “Make Baby A Headband” in PDF to print and place in a frame

After purchase I will message you with a few questions to complete the order.

* If this is a rush order there is an extra fee because all headband kits are made to order and I work on them on a weekly basis and not during the weekends. 
**Not all types of flowers, rosettes, & elastic are shown in the pictures
***Does come in more counts please message me for a custom order.


Thank you so much Courtney Jade Photography (http://courtneyjade.com/blog/) for providing these fabulous pictures from Jessica at Modern Moments Designs' baby Shower (http://modernmomentsdesigns.com)
